## Installation

<StackCmd>

```shell
fctl payments connectors install <%= providerLower %> config.json
```

```shell
curl -X POST "https://$STACK.formance.cloud/api/payments/connectors/<%= providerLower %>" \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
-d @config.json
```

